reviewText:
I don't know what the person was thinking that gave this 4 stars and said no phony actors.....
The "actors" in this badly done, badly shot, very badly acted movie could not act their way out of a paper bag.

This film is incredibly realistic, no phony actors or sets.  Full creep credits for the makeup.  The "Been There - Done That" hat really made me laugh towards the very end of the flick.  I would have given five stars but there wasn't any ghost sex.
